Cyclops Suit HD for Genesis 3 Male(s) is a complete, fully textured sci-fi armor set for Genesis 3 Male(s). This set includes eight clothing items and one prop, all richly textured with four easily combinable texture variations: camo blue, red, camo green and camo brown. All the textures are PBR (Physically Based Render) ready, to get the best looking renders in Iray and any other PBR compatible software packages.

All the items include HD detail morphs to get stunning render results in Daz Studio, and the set is fully compatible with 9 Genesis 3 Male shapes
